\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15155764\charrsid8024348 I suppose, 13 or 14. It\rquote s the kind of thing that Jewish families \endash  as you probably know - discuss around the Bar Mitzvah.
\par 
