\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5975301 Ronald:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15155764\charrsid8024348 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
\ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15155764\charrsid8024348 Yes.  Yes.  Well, it is quite a nice story actually.  My father didn\rquote t visit the primary school for a very long time, because Johnson \endash 
 the chauffeur- would take me there in the morning with Nurse, and then take Nurse back to the house.  I mean, it all sounds terribly bourgeois! (LAUGHS)  But it wasn\rquote t actually, because these \'85 
