\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15155764\charrsid8024348 In this very varied life that you\rquote ve had, and we\rquote 
ve only taken it up to about 1970, have you had time to do anything else apart from your work?  Have you had other hobbies or enthusiasms, or interests?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid5975301 Ronald:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15155764\charrsid8024348 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
