ve regarded my work as a sort of hobby, because I\rquote ve always had extremely enjoyable jobs!  I mean, my father always said, \'93You haven\rquote t got a job.  You\rquote ve got a permanent holiday\'94, about all my jobs (LAUGHS), because he\rquote 
d fought his way up from being a barber\rquote s boy to owning a wholesale warehouse!
