me during the daytime - and while I wouldn\rquote t want to be quoted on this - are not always as busy as men might be. I mean, it\rquote 
s quite difficult to talk to a farm worker, you might have to interrupt his work, but to talk to his wife, you can do it while she gets on with her work, you can follow her round the house and stuff.
