\i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15155764\charrsid8024348 The Sociological Review}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid15155764\charrsid8024348 , and Keele owned }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
